Purpose (AgDR-0072): used by the Clinical Co-Pilot module's source-chip bbox
overlay (interface/modules/custom_modules/oe-module-clinical-copilot/public/copilot.js,
showBboxOverlay) to render PDF page snippets with overlay rectangles indicating
where in the source document a cited fact came from.

Why vendored: cdnjs has been a documented supply-chain compromise vector
(cf. WordPress polyfill.io / Cloudflare CDN tampering incidents). Vendoring
under same-origin + SRI eliminates the third-party trust requirement and
makes a tampered file fail-closed in the browser instead of silently
executing.

Apache-2.0 attribution requirements satisfied by:
